@startuml
title ArcHub CMS - Versioning Application Service
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

actor "Content editor" as Editor
actor "Maintenance worker" as Worker
component "Admin routes\nweb.routes" as Routes
component "ArcHubVersioningService\napplication.versioning" as Versioning
component "ArcHubDomainEvent\ndomain.events" as Events
component "ArcHubCMSService\ncompatibility API" as CMS
database "SQLite CMS store" as DB

Editor --> Routes : view history,\nopen JSON,\nrestore version
Worker --> Versioning : cleanup policy command
Routes --> Versioning : versions / version /\nrestore / cleanup
Versioning --> CMS : list_versions()\nrestore_version()\ncleanup_content_versions()
CMS --> DB : archub_content_versions\narchub_content_nodes\narchub_content_activity
Versioning --> Events : content.version.restored\ncontent.versions.cleaned
Versioning --> Routes : VersioningOperationResult
Routes --> Editor : redirect or JSON payload
@enduml
